data.description: Convenient to both Lafayette and Carthage, this home and 24x24 shop sit on 14.07+/- acres. A covered front porch looks out over the wonderfully shaded front yard while the rest of this property is a hunter's paradise. This 3 bed 2 bath home features a split bedroom layout, master bedroom with full bath & walk-in closet, kitchen with separate dining room, large living room, and patio area out back. If quiet country living is what you have been looking for this listing is a must see. Please provide 24 hour notice for showing appointments.
